org.apache.mesos.scheduler

Class DefaultScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.mesos.scheduler.DefaultScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer

    public class DefaultScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observer
    This scheduler when provided with a ServiceSpecification will deploy the service and recover from encountered faults when possible. Changes to the ServiceSpecification will result in rolling configuration updates, or the creation of new Tasks where applicable.
